<apex:page standardController="Booking__c" renderAs="pdf" showHeader="false" applyBodyTag="false" applyHtmlTag="false" extensions="demandController" action="{!getTotalCost}">
    <html>
        <head>
            <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
            <style type="text/css">
                @page {
                size:A4 portrait;
                margin-bottom: 200px;
                margin-top: 200px;
                }
            </style>
        </head>
        
        <body >
             <div style="font-size: 17px;"><br/><br/><br/><br/>
               
                <p>
                    To<br/>
                    The Branch Manager<br/>
                    State Bank of India<br/>
                    Bangalore.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Dear Sir / Madam,  
                </p>
                <p>
                     I/We, M/s <b>Project Name:{!Booking__c.Project__c}</b>, here by certify that:                </p>
                <p>
                    
                    1. I / We have transferable rights to the property described below, which has been allotted to {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c	},<apex:repeat value="{!Booking__c.Co_Applicants__r}" var="p">
                        {!p.Name} ,                       
                    </apex:repeat>  herein after referred to as “the purchasers”, subject to the due and proper performance
                    and compliances of all the terms and conditions of the Allotment Letter / Sale Agreement dated - <apex:outputText value="{0, DATE, dd'-'MM'-'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!Booking__c.Sale_Agreement_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText> (herein after referred to as the “sale document”).
                </p>
                <p>
                    Description of the property:
                </p>
                 <table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="5">
                     <tr>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">{Plot No / House No}</th>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">{!Booking__c.Unit_NumberFor__c}</th>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">Building No / Name</th>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">{!Booking__c.Project__c}</th>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">Project Address</th>
                         <th style="font-weight: bold;">{!Booking__c.Project_Address__c}</th>
                     </tr>
                 </table>
                <p style="text-align:justify;">
                    2. That the total consideration for this transaction is Rs.{!TotalcostStr} (Rupees {!AmountInWords} towards sale document. 
                </p>
                <p style="text-align:justify;">
                  3. The title of the property described above is clear, marketable and free from all encumbrances and doubts. 
                </p>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                    4. I / We confirm that I / We have no objection whatsoever to the said purchasers, at their own costs, charges,
                    risks and consequences mortgaging the said property to STATE BANK OF INDIA (herein after referred to as “the Bank”)
                    as security for the amount advanced by the Bank to them subject to the due and proper performance and compliances of
                    all the terms and conditions of the sale document by the said purchasers.


                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                  5. We have not borrowed funds from any financial institutions and have no loan on construction. 
                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                   6. After creation of proper charge / mortgage and after receipt of the copies there of and after receipt of proper nomination 
                    in favour of the Bank, from the said purchasers, we are agreeable to accept State Bank of India as a nominee of the above named 
                    purchaser for the property described above and once the nomination favoring the Bank has been registered and advice sent to the Bank 
                    of having done so, I / We note not to change the same without the written NOC of the Bank. 
                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                   7. After creation of charge / mortgage and after receipt of the copies thereof and after receipt of the proper nomination in favour of
                    the Bank, from the above named purchaser, I / We undertake to inform the society about the Bank’s charge on the said flats and when the
                    society is formed. 
                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                   8. Please note that the payment for this transaction should be made by crossed cheque / Transfer of funds favoring SOWPARNIKA PROJECTS-  
                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                    Name: {!Booking__c.Account_Type__c} , {!Booking__c.Builder_Account_Number__c} , {!Booking__c.Project_Bank_Name__c}, IFSC Code: {!Booking__c.IFSC_Code__c}, Branch: {!Booking__c.Project_Bank_Branch__c}.
                </P>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                    9. In case of cancellation of the sale agreement for any reason, I/ We shall refund the amount by crossed cheque favouring the Bank A/c and forward
                    the same to you directly.
                </P>
                <P>
                   10. The signatory to this letter draws authority to sign this undertaking on behalf of the company  
                </P>
               
                <P>
                    Yours faithfully,
                </P>
                <P>
                    For {!Booking__c.Company_Name__c}
                </P>
                <P>
                   {!Booking__c.Owner.Name}
                </P>
                <P>
                    {!Booking__c.Owner_Designation__c}
                </P>
                 <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>
                <P style="text-align:justify;">
                    The said Bank to release the particular plot to {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c},<apex:repeat value="{!Booking__c.Co_Applicants__r}" var="p">
                        {!p.Name} ,                       
                    </apex:repeat>  and accordingly, the amount
                    may be released in our favour with Escrow account no. {!Booking__c.Builder_Account_Number__c}.  We also confirm that the Plot No.{!Booking__c.Unit_NumberFor__c}, {!Booking__c.Project__c}, Which is being sold to {!Booking__c.First_Applicant_Name__c}, falls within sanctioned plan.
                </P>
                <P>
                    Yours faithfully,
                </P>
                <P>
                    For {!Booking__c.Company_Name__c}
                </P>
                <P>
                    {!Booking__c.Owner.Name}
                </P>
                <P>
                    {!Booking__c.Owner_Designation__c})
                </P>
            
            </div>
        </body>
    </html>
</apex:page>